    {
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Step through each colour:\n  R: ing2=R- (ing2 has R-), ing4=R+ (ing3+ing6=R-: both share R-; ing3+ing4=neutral \u2192 ing4 has R+)\n      \u2192 opposite signs \u2192 skip.\n  G: ing2=G- (ing2+ing6=G-: both share G-), ing4=G- (ing4 has G-; ing3+ing4=neutral \u2192 ing3 has G+; ing3+ing4=neutral \u2192 ing4 has G-)\n      \u2192 SAME sign - \u2192 G- resolves."
    },
